nodes.text: A skilled Drabatan served as a mechanic on staff at the Resistance base on the planet D'Qar.

The Drabatan was first mentioned in the 2018 reference book Star Wars: Alien Archive. The non-canon television series LEGO Star Wars: All-Stars later identified the Drabatan as Ka-Pao. In All-Stars, he is voiced by Fred Tatasciore.
